Source: ghfaxviewer
Section: graphics
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Wolfgang Sourdeau <Wolfgang@ultim.net>
Build-Depends: debmake, libtiffg3-dev, libgtk1.2-dev | libgnome-dev
Standards-Version: 3.5.0

Package: ghfaxviewer-gtk
Section: graphics
Priority: optional
Replaces: gfaxviewer
Conflicts: gfaxviewer, ghfaxviewer-gnome
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
description: The GNU HaliFAX - Viewer
 This is the GNU HaliFAX Viewer, a component of GNU HaliFAX which will
 help you look at the TIFF g3/g4 fax files produced by HylaFAX
 .
 The GNU HaliFAX will be a complete free client package for HylaFAX
 and maybe for other fax systems in the future.
 It is intended to run on both the Win32 platform and the GNU system.
 .
 This is the GTK+-only version. For the GNOME version, please install the
 ghfaxviewer-gnome package instead.

Package: ghfaxviewer-gnome
Section: graphics
Priority: optional
Replaces: gfaxviewer
Conflicts: gfaxviewer, ghfaxviewer-gtk
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Suggests: gfax
description: The GNU HaliFAX - Viewer
 This is the GNU HaliFAX Viewer, a component of GNU HaliFAX which will
 help you look at the TIFF g3/g4 fax files produced by HylaFAX
 .
 The GNU HaliFAX will be a complete free client package for HylaFAX
 and maybe for other fax systems in the future.
 It is intended to run on both the Win32 platform and the GNU system.
 .
 This is the GNOME version. If you only have GTK+ installed, please install
 the ghfaxviewer-gtk package instead.
